r than on [e5]. I also feel White's queen is better on [c2], as then we then cannot play ...[g6] that easily.} 19. Qxb2 c5 20. Ng3 g6 $10 {[%cal Gh6h5,Gh5h4] We have a comfortable position with active pieces. We can continue with ...[h5]-[h4] on the kingside.} *

