$1 21. h4 Qxh4 $3 {This is the beauty of the Botvinnik variations. Our king may look weak, but at least we have a lot of pieces around it.} 22. Rxa7+ Kb6 $1 {Other moves are bad because they allow White to give up their rook on the a-file to get the queen into the game.} 23. Ra6+ Nxa6 24. gxh4 Rdg8+ 25. Kh2 Rxh4# *

