+ Kb8 20. Qb5+ {is the earlier mentioned draw by repetition.}) 19... Qf3 $1 {We control all the checks on the queenside while White is screwed, as their king is stuck in the centre.} 20. O-O Rxh2 $19 {Mate follows along the h-file.} *

