onent.} 27. Nxd4 cxd4 28. Re5 Rg6 $10 {[%csl Gb4,Gc4,Gd4][%cal Gg6c6] We will get our rook to [c6] and start pushing our queenside pawns. All results are possible here, and it will be a very exciting game.} *

