 the piece on our terms and will also grab the pawn on [h2]. All of this happened in my game ½- ½ Wang, S -Arjun, K Wch U18 Mumbai 2019. Surprisingly, White knew this line till the end, and we had to agree to a draw in a few more mores.} *

