ck the pawn with ...[Nb4]. As long as White's king is still on [e1] we will have enough resources.} 11. Nb3 Qd8 12. cxd5 Nb4 $36 {[%cal Gb4c2,Gf6d5,Rg7b2] We are threatening to jump into [c2], but also ...[Nfd5] is a big threat. The bishop on [g7] will be unleashed and there are a lot of weaknesses on the queenside for White.} *

